〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , of which this Polycarpus had the Governement, and a Bishop doubtlesse. In the which place 〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , is conforme most fully to the 〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 of Saint Paul, differing no otherwise then the verbe and participle.
